<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" face="Arial, sans-serif"><i>Chartered By&nbsp;The British Schools&nbsp;Foundation<br></i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" face="Arial, sans-serif"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"></font></div><span lang="en-GB" style="text-align: start;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><div style="margin: 0px;"><font color="#002060" size="3" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our attention which may affect your children.</span><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span id="gmail-docs-internal-guid-d1dab416-f5fd-cf19-7e49-78f1d9ec4b37"><br></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font color="#222222"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of Glandular fever in a pupil in our school. Glandular fever is a type of viral infection that mostly affects young adults. Common symptoms include fever, swollen glands, a sore throat and fatigue. It can be easily</span> treated with medication, good personal hygiene, general cleanliness and rest.</font><br><br><font color="#222222">We are taking all precautions necessary at school including:</font><br><ul><li style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Ensuring all school premises, furniture, carpets, bathrooms and canteens are thoroughly and deeply cleaned and disinfected daily</li><li>Children wash their hands throughout the day and always before and after meals and use of the bathrooms. &nbsp;</li></ul></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">If you believe your child has Glandular fever, please seek medical treatment, follow hygiene procedures at home and keep them away from school if they are experiencing any signs of discomfort.<br><br>For further information about Glandular fever, please see the link below:<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Glandular-fever/Pages/Introduction.aspx" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: none;"><span style="text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Glandular-fever/Pages/Introduction.aspx</span></a></p></div><font color="#000000" size="3" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; margin: 0px;"><br></div></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">Kind Regards&nbsp;</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">Adam Johnson&nbsp;</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;">Headteacher</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></div></font></span><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font></div></div>]]></td>
